{
  "stem": "21308.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That in turn meant that we had to think like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My job was with the brigade commander and I controlled the artillery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that meant my own guns and any others which had been allocated to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the River Rhine, that was well over 800.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the Aller, it certainly included medium guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then you chose targets for those guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you always had to be in the right place to do the job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was the brigade commander's gunner, [INAUDIBLE] Roberts, and I knew that the best thing I could do was to stay in his pocket.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we used to go and he used to run everywhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very fit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to have to run, as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had about 90 pounds on our back in wireless equipment, batteries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had nothing except he had a Garand rifle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you now what a Garand rifle is?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's an automatic rifle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was a deadly shot with it, deadly shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a good chap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I mean, we always went over with the-- either immediately behind the leading wave or with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --we worked at night, which meant that from a gunner's point of view, making any reference to targets and that sort of thing was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --one of the-- one of the skills which we adopted and we worked very hard at was reading air photographs, and so much so that we would map a course out because we tried to break through and then attack the enemy from the rear.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would-- through the air photographs, you can read the sort of land where are were planning to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
